    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Some supportive teachers , who help you throughout all the difficulties",
          "name": "Shreya",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the fact that my college facilities for differently abled students to study here",
          "name": "Nidhi Chouhan",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like punctuality and discipline of departments in my college.",
          "name": "Nidhi Chouhan",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Even this is only girls college but yhe strength of the students are high",
          "name": "Soniya arya",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Class are up yo date.. Every classes are held on time and  daily nad there for sc st the books are given to them on id cards",
          "name": "Soniya arya",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The staff is very working and there are different departments gor different subjects... And specialized places aur window aur every work...",
          "name": "Soniya arya",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The best thing about my college is that classes held on a regular basis and professor pay attention to students regarding their career goals their future goals etc",
          "name": "Isha Pandey",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the programs they held and encouragement they show through there program to students",
          "name": "Roshni",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The environment is good clam and very studious moreover it have canteen",
          "name": "Roshni",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like how supportive professor are they really helps u out guide u whenever u need there help u can always rely on there help",
          "name": "Roshni",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Poor management , they should be fare enough towards every student which clearly they are not.",
          "name": "Shreya",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "I hate the fact that my college's campus is very small especially playground",
          "name": "Nidhi Chouhan",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "I hate the huge time gaps between lectures in my college",
          "name": "Nidhi Chouhan",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "I dislike the ruder behaviour of few professors there",
          "name": "Nidhi Chouhan",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Quick actions are not taken on student's complaint",
          "name": "Isha Pandey",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "And also they didn't pay much attention to cleanliness",
          "name": "Isha Pandey",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The thing i disliked about my college is poor management",
          "name": "Isha Pandey",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Safety wise not good even though they tried to maintain it but still there is loophole within the college as a girls college it should focus on safety",
          "name": "Roshni",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Washroom are not good and sanitary work is not done in college need to focus on that",
          "name": "Roshni",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Faculty is not good specially when it comes to documentary work moreover they do help but still i find it could be lot more better",
          "name": "Roshni",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        }
      ]
